WEBVTT

00:01.880 --> 00:07.800
It’s no good... I don’t know... what to do.

00:09.400 --> 00:13.460
Yoshida-kun... you’ve betrayed me, too?

00:14.840 --> 00:17.400
You were laughing at me from the beginning, weren’t you?

00:17.730 --> 00:19.800
You and all those jerks in the lab.

00:21.240 --> 00:27.660
I leaned on you and cried and told you what made me angry, and you took everything I confided in you and told everybody and laughed with them.

00:29.660 --> 00:35.480
I don’t want to believe this, but I caught you in the act.

00:37.260 --> 00:39.620
You were the only person I had, Yoshida-kun.

00:41.220 --> 00:43.200
You were just a shallow man.

00:45.310 --> 00:47.350
How can you be so dumb, Touko?

00:52.000 --> 00:58.400
Who is that? Is someone talking to me? That’s impossible. Nobody is here.

01:00.130 --> 01:03.150
It’s me. Touko.

01:06.080 --> 01:13.350
Touko? I’m Touko! Stop! Who’s trying to torment me like this? Please stop!
